{
  "stem": "2581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father said that the rabbi just told everyone that wherever there is a minion of Jews is a holy place and you can pray.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You disregard all the crosses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After three days, Biebow, Himmler's son-in-law, came to our town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he separated-- you know, we went all in one group, the way Mengele did in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, everyone would come in front of him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would say, you go back to the church-- to the church.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those that went back to the church, these were being sent away to Himmler for  extermination.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The others were sent into a field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a ravine, because we were-- stay-- stayed there overnight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly the number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's someplace between 600 or 800 people, closer to 600.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I really don't know and I wouldn't want to mistake the number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we stayed overnight and then the next day we were taken to  the railroad and traveled to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really-- we came at the central place where we sorted out, you know, we were sent to different places to stay.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't-- didn't take anything except what was on our back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing-- no package-- not the smallest package in the hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only what we had on our back-- back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we knew that those-- because those that they selected to Lodz-- to Ghetto Lodz-- were only strong people, young people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And here I have to-- and I remember that I was wearing pullover blouse that my father made for me in a navy fabric.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I had stuck a white needle-- I mean a needle with white thread.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
